contentrichtext.text: '''Bayside''' may refer to a number of places: In the '''United States''': *[[Bayside, California]] *[[Bayside High School (disambiguation)]], several schools in the U.S. and Canada *[[Bayside Marketplace]], Miami, Florida *[[Bayside (Jeanerette, Louisiana)]], [[List of RHPs in LA|listed on the NRHP in Louisiana]] *[[Bayside Historic District (Bayside, Maine)]], [[List of RHPs in ME|listed on the NRHP in Maine]] *Bayside, a residential zone in [[Northport, Maine]] *Bayside, a neighborhood in [[Portland, Maine]] *[[Bayside, Queens]], New York, a neighborhood in New York City **[[Bayside (LIRR station)]], rail station in Queens *[[Bayside, Texas]] *[[Bayside, Wisconsin]] * In '''Canada''': *[[Bayside, Charlotte County, New Brunswick]] *[[Bayside, Newfoundland and Labrador]] *[[Bayside, Nova Scotia]] *[[Bayside, Ontario]] *[[Bayside, Prince Edward Island]] *[[Bayside, Westmorland County, New Brunswick]] '''Other places''': *[[Bayside Comprehensive School]], Gibraltar *[[Bayside, Dublin]], in Ireland *[[City of Bayside]], in the Australian State of Victoria, in the suburbs of Melbourne '''Other uses''': *[[Bayside (album)|''Bayside'' (album)]], by Bayside *[[Bayside (band)]], an American punk rock band *''[[Bayside Shakedown]]'', a Japanese TV series *''[[Bayside Shakedown: The Movie]]'', a movie based on the TV series *''[[Bayside Shakedown 2]]'', a second movie based on the TV series {{disambig}} [[Category:Place name disambiguation pages]]
